    - Read and execute the [prerequisites.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/prerequisites.mdc) rule file.
    - Read and execute the [website-analysis.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/website-analysis.mdc) on the URL passed
    - Read the best practices for creating a Scrapy spider contained in the file @scrapy.mdc. 
    - One requested to create a scraper, follow the instructions in the file [scraper-models.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/scraper-models.mdc) for the coherent scraper type requested.
    
